{"tid":1379171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[明食女 吹啊] 呢兩個月，大家係前線食左幾多條女？","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:29:24.000Z","uid":52658,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"365a07bb766e556cda07d2f694d281e8f598f4d9","tid":1379171,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:53:55.000Z","msg":"我食左兩條警犬人妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路抽插佢 一邊屌到啪啪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後大巴大巴車落果兩隻隻犬科生物塊面度<br />\n同佢講 我而家係食你老婆啊你吹鳩我漲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 綠帽仔<br />\n<br />\n警畜死全家<br />\n你班社會既廢人 食狗餅食到懵撚左啊？屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地一撚定有報應 咁樣打市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>以後再比我聽到邊撚個撐警 我就屌邊個</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e50b3da7c616f74be1cafbf0bc21acc25d7be606","tid":1379171,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:55:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc7da2f1901cefb895f53ecfa3e88486f8e544fa","tid":1379171,"uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"今日真係好撚火滾<br />\n對唔住 咁多位兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自守先 我原本以為今日和平集會<br />\n所以同個frd去左電莖節睇人打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到我知道左已經好大件事 好心痛您地 好想喊<br />\n<br />\n好多謝係銅記果位兄弟 你見到我兩手空空鳩fing乜都無<br />\n你擔心我安全 截住我唔比我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝您 我呢一世都會記得呢幕 真係想喊<br />\n因為您地 我好自豪我係香港人<br />\n希望咁多位可以平安無事出返黎<br />\n<br />\n記住我無野講 我唔解鎖同埋我要口供紙副本<br />\n<br />\n